{"format":"tiptap/v1","updatedAt":"2026-06-21T00:27:15.330Z","doc":{"type":"doc","content":[{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Anthropic's Prompt Generator"},{"type":"text","text":" is a built-in console tool that lets you "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"generate production-ready prompts in the developer console"},{"type":"text","text":" by describing what you want to achieve. Claude uses prompt engineering techniques like chain-of-thought reasoning to create effective, precise, and reliable prompts automatically."}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Think of it as "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Claude writing your prompts for you"},{"type":"text","text":" — a game-changer for both beginners and experienced prompt engineers."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"What the Prompt Generator Does"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Core Capabilities"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"You can now generate production-ready prompts in the Anthropic Console. Describe what you want to achieve, and Claude will use prompt engineering techniques like chain-of-thought reasoning to create an effective, precise, and reliable prompt.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Key features:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Agent-assisted prompt generation"},{"type":"text","text":" — Claude writes professional prompts for you\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Uses prompt engineering techniques"},{"type":"text","text":" — Chain-of-thought reasoning built into the generator\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Production-ready output"},{"type":"text","text":" — Creates effective, precise, and reliable