ws, missing information"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Expected output:"},{"type":"text","text":" Production-ready prompt with structured output schema and validation instructions."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"How It Works (Behind the Scenes)"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"The Long Prompt Technique"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"The prompt generator is based on a long prompt that itself uses many of the techniques already mentioned.\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"What this means:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- The generator itself is powered by a "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"detailed system prompt"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- This system prompt uses "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"advanced prompt engineering techniques"},{"type":"text","text":" (CoT, XML tags, examples, etc.)\n- The generator applies these techniques to "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"create your prompts"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"It's meta-prompting:"},{"type":"text","text":" A well-designed prompt that generates other well-designed prompts."}]},{"type":"horizontalRule"},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":2},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"Benefits"}]},{"type":"heading","attrs":{"level":3},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"For Beginners"}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"\"This feature is designed to help users who are new to prompt engineering\""}]},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"Benefits:"},{"type":"text","text":"\n- "},{"type":"text","marks":[{"type":"bold"}],"text":"No expertise needed"},{"type":"text","t